Subject:The magic of romance
I do not know what to start with that’s why I'll start by telling you about myself. 
I find myself quite a knowledgeable and clever girl, also I am  very nice and responsive. 

I enjoy simple things. I am very good at cooking and drawing.. 
It seems to be foolish to describe the man whom I want to see by my side. 
I am looking for normal, realistic man. For me it is very important to meet my other half. Though, I can say for sure that appearance is far from being very important. 
The inner beauty is much more important than beauty of the body. I want my man to be serious, communicative and very attentive. 
